metadata.name: Brave New
metadata.description:
This image was created with the help of AI while traveling at an altitude of 38000 feet somewhere over Iowa. 

It is the first token on a brand new contract created on Manifold while traveling somewhere over Minnesota. 

Finally, this image was minted while traveling at 475 mph somewhere over  North Dakota.

All in the space of two hours and completed on an mobile phone.

Let that sink in.
